 Although they are related, Lunaporin has never been mentioned alongside <a href="/wiki/Taikin" title="Taikin">Taikin</a> nor <a href="/wiki/Kamikazin" title="Kamikazin">Kamikazin</a> in any legends. It is thought to be due to very few sightings or encounters, leading to it fading into obscurity. It lets out a a spine-chilling howl when the moon is at its highest point in the sky.
